2 Weeks Loving You! The days and nights mesh together and I have no idea the date, but I love every minute staring at you Olivia.

You have the biggest personality ALREADY! You are hilarious, expressive, loving, and playful.

You giggle when you get ready to eat, you love mom’s milk, and you love baths!

I think I changed your diaper 10x today already… and the night is young. But I love our special moments together ❤️.

You can now see mommy and you reach for my face. You are a tummy time pro, and you love your black and white photos!

Every day you develop and change and part of me loves it and the other part wants you to stay this little forever. I love you my little peanut, princess, bean….the names keep coming 🤣.

@leonardobatistella ❤️

I’m so honored and grateful to have been awarded the “Rising Star Award for 2022” @sevengablesrealestate !

Real estate has always been a passion of mine since I was little. Open houses were a favorite pastime with my mom and late dad on the weekends.

If you know me, you know i’m an old soul and would rather hang with the adults all weekend looking at new construction homes and memorizing the floor plans. I remember schooling my dad on the different floor plans and facades! (he didn’t like this you could imagine 🤣, I was probably 10)

Well, 20 years later i’ve dived right into what I knew i always loved and just was too afraid to start! I am so glad I took a leap of faith and joined @sevengablesrealestate with the best mentors and the best community of agents!

I told Leo last night, that at Seven Gables, we are all family. There are no egos walking around. Everyone is loyal, honest and giving to each other. To be surrounded by coworkers that feel like family is a true blessing! I am so happy to have found my second home 🏡!

For all of your real estate needs, feel free to contact me anytime to chat! Also, follow my realtor account @chrissyrealty for market updates and more!

Saved the best for last 😅! Can’t believe our precious peanut is 5 months old already! (1 week ago 😂)

She blows us away every day with her new skills! This girl is sitting up all by herself already, rolling around, and eating her toes!

She even reaches up high during tummy time, and is getting ready to pull herself forward!

She is determined and definitely has a voice in our house! She babbles all day and is definitely the center of our universe! 💕

She is sleeping amazingly!!! Sleep training took one day with her 😍. She was ready! Next week we are starting some solid foods!

Can’t wait to see what she accomplishes next! 💗 I love you Olivia 🥰!

@leonardobatistella

Just like that…. we have a one year old! I feel like i just gave birth, so I have no idea where this year went, but it has been amazing to see her grow!!

She is fearless, determined, smart, loving, caring, and strong as nails. She loves ALL food 🙏🏻 Praise the Lord!

She loves MUSIC 🎶 AND DANCING 💃 Like her mama and dada! 💕

She runs laps around the kitchen after each meal 😂 she never stops or sits still… like her Momma and Nana @karenelizr56

She gives the best hugs 🥰 and head butts 😂 working on the kisses 😘 More of a bang in the forehead for now 🙈. Just praying she doesn’t do this to other kiddos 😂.

She loves her friends and loves to show people her toys and share her food 💕 I just love her more than words will ever describe.

Olivia is more than I could ever have dreamed of. She’s more than I ever hoped for in a child. We are so blessed with her amazing spirit and soul.

She truly was born with a beautiful, kind, happy soul. Thank you Lord 🙏🏻 

We love you Olivia 🥰 @leonardobatistella
